    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40-2018 applicability matrix. Hemolysis benchmark comparison demonstrates mean error of 8.3% with all predictions within acceptance band. Grid independence confirmed with GCI < 2% on production mesh. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all five operating points. Credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
